title: BRIEF-China's games company Ourpalm expects 9-month net profit to rise 25-45 pct y/y
text:
Oct 14 Ourpalm Co Ltd
* Says expects 9-month net profit to rise 25-45 percent y/y to 254.3-295.0 million yuan ($40.07-46.48 million)
Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/1RGzVzy
